nodes.text: Kway Teow was the capital city on the tropical world of Felucia, during the era of the Clone Wars. During that conflict, Commerce Guild Presidente Shu Mai maintained a secure compound just outside the city borders. Upon arrival on Felucia, Shu Mai landed at an executive landing platform in Kway Teow, from which it was a short speeder ride to her fortified compound.
Char kway teow is a popular noodle dish in Malaysia and Singapore; 'Kway Teow' literally means 'flat noodles'.
